<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Progetti - Angelo Alberico</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        nav {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 3rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #667eea;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .projects-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .project-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 2rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .project-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
        }

        .project-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .project-meta {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #999;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .project-card p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .project-tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .tag {
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid #667eea;
        }

        .project-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .project-links a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .project-links a:hover {
            color: #764ba2;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/">About</a>
        <a href="/projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="/repositories">Repositories</a>
        <a href="/cv">CV</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>I Miei Progetti</h1>

        <div class="projects-grid">
            <!-- GottaBattleEmAll -->
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>GottaBattleEmAll</h3>
                <div class="project-meta">Progetto Universitario | 2024-2025</div>
                <p>Un'applicazione web interattiva per il gioco di battaglia Pokémon. Il progetto integra frontend moderno 
                con backend robusto, implementando sistemi di login, gestione dei pokémon, e battaglie in tempo reale.</p>
                <div class="project-tags">
                    <span class="tag">React</span>
                    <span class="tag">Node.js</span>
                    <span class="tag">MongoDB</span>
                    <span class="tag">WebSocket</span>
                    <span class="tag">Authentication</span>
                </div>
                <div class="project-links">
                    <a href="https://github.com/Nakura125/GottaBattleEmAll" target="_blank">GitHub →</a>
                    <a href="#">Demo →</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- WRF4Salerno -->
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>WRF4Salerno</h3>
                <div class="project-meta">Collaborazione ISISLab | 2024-2025</div>
                <p>Sistema di previsione meteorologica ad alta risoluzione per il territorio campano. Collaborazione con 
                ISISLab per l'analisi e la visualizzazione di dati meteorologici usando il modello WRF (Weather Research and Forecasting).</p>
                <div class="project-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Python</span>
                    <span class="tag">Data Science</span>
                    <span class="tag">Meteorologia</span>
                    <span class="tag">Visualization</span>
                </div>
                <div class="project-links">
                    <a href="https://github.com/ISISLab" target="_blank">ISISLab →</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Portfolio Website -->
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>Portfolio Website</h3>
                <div class="project-meta">Progetto Personale | 2025</div>
                <p>Il sito che stai visualizzando! Un portfolio moderno realizzato con Astro, con integrazione automatica 
                delle repository GitHub e design responsivo. Ospitato su GitHub Pages.</p>
                <div class="project-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Astro</span>
                    <span class="tag">GitHub API</span>
                    <span class="tag">GitHub Pages</span>
                    <span class="tag">Responsive Design</span>
                </div>
                <div class="project-links">
                    <a href="https://github.com/Nakura125/angeloalberico.github.io" target="_blank">GitHub →</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
